What is Ranter?

Are you tired of struggling to find the perfect rental property? Look no further than Ranter! Our platform provides tenants with the most current and authentic reviews from previous renters, helping you to find your ideal home. Say goodbye to the guesswork and frustration of the rental search process and say hello to the ease and convenience of Ranter!

Requirements of the application:

What does Ranter do?

Ranter allows two types of users:

  1. Reviewer: This user will be the tenant who reviews the place they currently live in.
  2. Review audiences: This user will be the one who browses through the system and finds reviews of the place they will potentially rent in the future.

What are the requirements?

There will be 3 types of properties and aspects that can be reviewed:

  • Sharehouse: Review the Landlord, shared common area (bathroom, kitchen, living room), tenant’s rented room.
  • Apartment: Review the Landlord, tenant’s rented room, building maintenance.
  • Student Accommodation: Review the Landlord/agent, tenant’s rented room.

No offensive words are allowed. A filter will be implemented to prevent their usage.

); } export default App;
